
Intha Veenailu Theriyathu
Athai Seithavan Yaranru
Yen Sontha Pillaiyum Ariyathu
Athai Thanthavan Yaranru
Enakkkul Azhuthu Rasikinren
Irandiyum Madyil Sumakinren

Malaiyil Vazhuki Vizhuntha Nathiku adaikalam thanthathu kadal thane
Karuvil Vazhuki Vizhantha Kodikku Adaikalam thanthathu Kilai thane
Engo azhutha kanner thodaika Engo oru viral irukathe
Pavam kuruvikal thagam theera gangai innum nadakirathu

Sontham Pantham Enpathu Ellam Solli therintha Murai thane
Sorkam Naragam Enpathu Ellam Soozhnelai kodutha niram thane
Ullam enbathu sariyay irunthal ulagam muzhutum inikarathu
Uthirip pokum poo kooda uyir vazhathan thudikarathu
